Hey little guy! @animaledventures show us the pouch, that acts as a warm, safe place for joeys. 🙏🏽 We can post your photos in our account, follow the link in our bio: @nomadfervor and we will select your pictures

📽 @animaledventures 🦘

At around six months, when a baby kangaroo is sufficiently well developed, it will leave the pouch for short periods, returning when it needs to feed. Did you know that?
